<div class="ticker-bar">
  <span class="ticker-inner">🔴 BREAKING: Parliament passes Digital India Infrastructure Bill &nbsp;|&nbsp; Sensex ▲ 312 pts · Nifty ▲ 98 pts &nbsp;|&nbsp; India beats Australia 3-1 in Test series &nbsp;|&nbsp; ISRO deploys GSAT-20 successfully &nbsp;|&nbsp; USD/INR: ₹83.42 &nbsp;|&nbsp; India ranks #5 globally by GDP &nbsp;|&nbsp; Renewable energy hits 200 GW milestone &nbsp;|&nbsp; Delhi AQI: 186 (Moderate) &nbsp;|&nbsp; PM Modi inaugurates new AIIMS in Jammu &nbsp;|&nbsp; India-France sign defence partnership agreement</span>
